cu.explanation_en: Changing the AMF IP address to a different subnet (10.0.0.1) creates an IP range conflict, making the AMF unreachable from the CU due to routing misconfiguration.

du.explanation_en: Changing the local N address to a different subnet (10.0.0.1) creates an IP range conflict, making the CU unreachable from the DU due to routing misconfiguration.
